{
  "text": "Polecats were trapped under English Nature license 20052467, and mink were rereleased for monitoring under Department for Environment, Food, and Rural Affairs license WCA/06/4. All procedures were carried out under United Kingdom Home Office licenses PPL30/1826, PIL30/6530, and PIL30/6917; were approved by Oxford University Zoology Department Ethical Review Committee; and met guidelines approved by the American Society of Mammalogists [CITATION_1] ).",
